{"tid":330291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個玩尻廣告電話嘅方法","createTime":"2017-07-21T05:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T05:35:22.000Z","uid":36811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3776e21f5001ff7e4bc64dee424bb96c052e83c1","tid":330291,"uid":36811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"早排忙緊果陣成日有廣告/騙案電話打黎<br />\n呢排放假無野做真係好得閒<br />\n應該點玩好？<br />\n<br />\n頭先 3111 5668 打黎<br />\n唔出聲就收左線<br />\n上網check 1 check 見到d人話係扮大眾銀行嘅詐騙電話<br />\n結果我打翻4x個電話比佢 佢終於聽我電話<br />\n但係由於我口才同急才太差<br />\n同佢溝通左半分鐘左右就完左<br />\n想問下各位巴絲打 點先可以玩耐d？"},{"pid":"5aef3e1e5c65ededc9fe3dce2c6300b60c5a088d","tid":330291,"uid":116181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"打過黎係女既先好玩"},{"pid":"6e8baf0eeccd6671ce8341cc3e8cf7cab74b69f8","tid":330291,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2d61ba260ed1680d72ab72a59caccef76afffc8","tid":330291,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打過黎係女既先好玩</blockquote><br />\n大陸老女人"},{"pid":"12ad3740f7f6cfd351ea45fe5b458ec133a76011","tid":330291,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打過黎係女既先好玩</blockquote><br />\n有啲把聲甜既，好係聽耐少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到最後reject 佢果吓，佢果把嬌嗲聲真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果聲沙果啲，我會叫佢休息下，飲返啖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7392cbc08ba982ecadc01e891fc045c9adcf2d62","tid":330291,"uid":36811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尻</span><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XBc6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXBc6b.png&h=88eefc41&s={SIZE}\" /> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鳩</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">果陣</span><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XBc6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXBc6b.png&h=88eefc41&s={SIZE}\" /> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嗰陣</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XBkTp.md.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXBkTp.md.png&h=f6a6fc4a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已改<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/132050_6182ba04880830a5484bc23222bd8648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F132050_6182ba04880830a5484bc23222bd8648.jpg&h=1d698dce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d988726925e13a186ba2c99a9b5360d9d6a3f613","tid":330291,"uid":36811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打過黎係女既先好玩</blockquote><br />\n有啲把聲甜既，好係聽耐少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到最後reject 佢果吓，佢果把嬌嗲聲真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果聲沙果啲，我會叫佢休息下，飲返啖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭先我打去嘅係老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b0402d145b843ca0dc326fb8250152ea3d2f0a","tid":330291,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:23:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3075d0ac460a6f85c389f8124ee200c317b7ee00","tid":330291,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:25:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7cccd75bec419e5e2934b0869b1176dace5a0b7","tid":330291,"uid":36811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日有人打黎話我一個月之前中獎 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：電話狗<br />\n電話狗：先生點解唔攞 係咪我地服務唔好<br />\n我：唔得閒 我係大陸住 <br />\n電話狗：我地係大陸好多地方都攞到 先生你係邊<br />\n我：齊齊哈爾 <br />\n電話狗：吓<br />\n靜左幾秒<br />\n電話狗：𡃁仔係咪玩野<br />\n之後Cut左我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前入境處打黎<br />\n我叫佢講廣東話 佢就爆seed鬧我再收我線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想可以好似楊岳橋咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16ac19ed477f7f3d3814879cd776adee0472c0f","tid":330291,"uid":33022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾日有人打黎話我一個月之前中獎 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：電話狗<br />\n電話狗：先生點解唔攞 係咪我地服務唔好<br />\n我：唔得閒 我係大陸住 <br />\n電話狗：我地係大陸好多地方都攞到 先生你係邊<br />\n我：齊齊哈爾 <br />\n電話狗：吓<br />\n靜左幾秒<br />\n電話狗：𡃁仔係咪玩野<br />\n之後Cut左我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前入境處打黎<br />\n我叫佢講廣東話 佢就爆seed鬧我再收我線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想可以好似楊岳橋咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尋日入境處都有打俾我，又話我有重要文件未攞<br />\n否則限制出境<br />\n咁我咪同佢傾下囉<br />\n有條蝗講蝗話同我傾，開頭我都好客氣<br />\n問下佢係邊度入境處，佢竟然話灣仔<br />\n我就用左我學左三十幾年嘅廣東話粗口屌到佢cut我線"}]}